    <entry>
      <title>相关配置</title>
      <link href="/post/45289.html"/>
      <url>/post/45289.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Linux"><a href="#Linux" class="headerlink" title="Linux"></a>Linux</h2><p>修改密码：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">passwd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改sshd_config文件:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi etc/ssh/sshd_config  <span class="comment">#ssh服务的配置文件</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>开启ssh服务:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">service ssh status  <span class="comment"># 查看状态，默认没打开</span></span><br><span class="line">service ssh start  <span class="comment"># 开启ssh服务，现在就可以用Xshell连接了</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Linux后台运行的方法：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">nohup</span> python -u train.py &gt; output.log 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看运行信息：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cat</span> output.log</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>验证脚本是否在后台运行：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ps aux | grep train.py</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>中止运行：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pkill -f download.py</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看磁盘空间：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">df</span> -h <span class="comment">#可以显示文件系统的总大小、已用空间、可用空间和挂载点等信息。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">du</span> -sh <span class="comment">#查看目录或文件占用磁盘空间的命令。</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Anaconda"><a href="#Anaconda" class="headerlink" title="Anaconda"></a>Anaconda</h2><p>删除虚拟环境：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda remove -n  需要删除的环境名 --all</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用镜像源：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install 包名称 -i https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
